<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .aboutme {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Styles for "myedu" section */
        .myedu {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Styles for "bgebs" and "sxc" */
        .bgebs,
        .sxc {
            display: flex;
          flex-direction : column;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Styles for "bgebs" section */
        .bgebs {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Styles for "bgebs-head" */
        .bgebs-head {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
          text-align :center;
        }

        /* Styles for "bgebs-body" */
        .bgebs-body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
        }

        /* Styles for "bgebs-img" */
        .bgebs-img {
            width: 60%;
          justify-content : center;
          
        }

        /* Styles for "slider" */
        .slider {
            width: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
          display : flex;
          flex-direction : row;
          margin-left : 10vw;

          
        }

        .slider img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            animation: slide 4s infinite;
          display : flex;
          flex-direction : row;
        }

        @keyframes slide {
            0% { transform: translateX(0%); }
            25% { transform: translateX(-120%); }
            50% { transform: translateX(-240%); }
            75% { transform: translateX(-300%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(-400%); }
        }

        /* Styles for "bgebs-text" */
        .bgebs-text {
            width: 40%;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
          
        }

        /* Styles for individual lines of text */
        .text-line {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="aboutme">
        <div class="myedu">
            <div class="bgebs">
                <div class="bgebs-head">BGEBS</div>
                <div class="bgebs-body">
                    <div class="bgebs-img">
                        <div class="slider">
                            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Image 1">
                            <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Image 2">
                            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Image 3">
                            <img src="https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/SUseaFJLlkWa6RbROi54RZ96YZRTTK7bKWnLEAuy9_ZwAtq2Y4vVhHWZ3pxr8ayYYS4=w526-h296-rw" alt="Image 4">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bgebs-text">
                        <div class="text-line">Line 1</div>
                        <div class="text-line">Line 2</div>
                        <div class="text-line">Line 3</div>
                        <div class="text-line">Line 4</div>
                        <div class="text-line">Line 5</div>
                        <div class="text-line">Line 6</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sxc">
          LoremIspuscsakjsaa saj asj
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
